[SPEAKER_01]: Admiral Chester Nimitz said of those who fought at Iwo Jima, and especially on that day, what is called D-Day at Iwo Jima, among the Americans who served on Iwo, uncommon valor was a common virtue.

11:51.391 --> 11:58.842
[SPEAKER_01]: And I'm sure you felt that way as you fought side by side beside the rest of the Marines and the other soldiers that were there.

11:59.294 --> 12:02.618
