12:47.911 --> 12:54.058
[SPEAKER_00]: We had left after Sarabache was secured to everybody's satisfaction.

12:54.098 --> 13:06.892
[SPEAKER_00]: The 28th Marines turned north and joined the rest of the 5th Marine Division, which was the 26th and the 27th Marines, and we being the 28th, joined them.

13:08.074 --> 13:12.399
[SPEAKER_00]: We were alongside of other divisions, the 3rd Marine Division and the 4th Marine Division.

13:13.480 --> 13:15.302
[SPEAKER_00]: It was the front line, and we were,

13:15.653 --> 13:27.165
[SPEAKER_00]: So we were moving up to fill in there when our convoy got stopped because of shell fire and I saw some folks that I knew in a mortar position

13:27.871 --> 13:32.898
