[SPEAKER_01]: And you went on, I believe, among your jobs in your retirement.

25:49.997 --> 25:52.121
[SPEAKER_01]: You were a salesman for a while, is that right?

25:52.141 --> 25:52.722
[SPEAKER_00]: A salesman.

25:52.762 --> 26:02.621
[SPEAKER_00]: I worked also for the Veterans Administration as a contact representative dealing with the veterans and their benefits with the VA.

26:02.982 --> 26:04.144
[SPEAKER_01]: Right, right.

