[SPEAKER_01]: And now you live here in Bryan and you are here in rural Bryan.

26:49.851 --> 26:52.474
[SPEAKER_01]: And love it.

26:52.494 --> 26:53.215
[SPEAKER_01]: And love it.

26:53.575 --> 26:54.817
[SPEAKER_01]: Absolutely.

